                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <p>Every summer, the city of Taza comes alive with magic and enthusiasm to host one of the most anticipated events of the year: the music festivals in the municipal garden. This festive occasion brings together thousands of people from all over the country and beyond to indulge in a true musical spectacle featuring several famous singers..</p>
