                            The festival kicks off in the early evening as the sun sets gently on the horizon. The first notes of music resonate, heralding the start of this awe-inspiring musical extravaganza. Singers, carefully chosen for their exceptional talents, take turns on stage, mesmerizing the audience with their enchanting voices and captivating performances.

