                                        <div class="accordion-body">
                                            The festivals in Taza feature a diverse lineup of famous singers and musicians from various genres, ranging from traditional Moroccan to international performers
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="accordion-item">
                                    <h4 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                                            Are there any special activities or interactions <br />with the artists during the festivals?
                                        </button>
                                    </h4>
                                    <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                                        <div class="accordion-body">
                                            Yes, during the festivals, there are opportunities for the audience to interact with the artists. Some artists may engage in meet-and-greet sessions, take photos with fans, and even invite selected audience members to sing along on stage.
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="destination-common-title">
                            <h4>Feel Free Ask This Place :</h4>
                        </div>
                        <div class="destination-form-container">
                            <form id="myForm">
                                <input type="text" id="name" placeholder="Your name" name="name" required autocomplete="off" />

                                <input type="text" id="phone" placeholder="Your phone" name="phone" required autocomplete="off" />

                                <input type="text" id="subject" placeholder="Your subject" name="subject" required autocomplete="off" />

                                <textarea id="question" placeholder="Write your Question" name="question" required autocomplete="off"></textarea>

                                <button type="button" id="submit">Send now</button>
                            </form>
                        </div>


                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- destination details -->
</div>


